(42, 23, 32, 42, 22, 37, 37, NULL, 'Connection of Transgressors Theme', 'Both passages emphasize being ''reckoned among the transgressors.'' The SOURCE verse mentions two malefactors, while the TARGET passage directly references this concept, linking the two contexts of Jesus'' crucifixion.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
