(42, 23, 33, 5, 21, 23, 23, NULL, 'Connection of Crucifixion and Accursed', 'This connection highlights the theme of being accursed, as seen in both passages. Luke''s mention of crucifixion aligns with Deuteronomy''s reference to being hanged as accursed of God.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
